yle:inherit;font-family:&quot;font-size:13.5pt;vertical-align:baseline;font-weight:inherit;line-height:27px;\">10</span><span style=\"font-style:inherit;font-family:宋体;font-size:13.5pt;vertical-align:baseline;font-weight:inherit;line-height:27px;\">日上网打印准考证。网址：</span><span style=\"font-style:inherit;font-family:inherit;font-size:9pt;vertical-align:baseline;font-weight:inherit;line-height:18px;\"><a href=\"http://www.graduate.neu.edu.cn/\"><span style=\"font-style:inherit;font-family:&quot;color:#444444;font-size:13.5pt;vertical-align:baseline;font-weight:inherit;line-height:27px;\">http://www.graduate.neu.edu.cn</span></a></span> \n</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"font-family:&quot;font-size:14px;vertical-align:baseline;color:#666666;text-indent:27.1pt;background:white;\">\n	<b><span style=\"font-style:inherit;font-family:宋体;font-size:13.5pt;vertical-align:baseline;font-weight:inherit;line-height:27px;\">六、考试</span></b><span style=\"font-style:inherit;font-family:inherit;font-size:9pt;vertical-align:baseline;font-weight:inherit;line-height:18px;\"></span> \n</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"font-family:&quot;font-size:14px;vertical-align:baseline;color:#666666;text-indent:27pt;background:white;\">\n	<span style=\"font-style:inherit;font-family:宋体;font-size:13.5pt;vertical-align:baseline;font-weight:inherit;line-height:27px;\">考试分初试和复试两个阶段。</span><span style=\"font-style:inherit;font-family:inherit;font-size:9pt;vertical-align:baseline;font-weight:inherit;line-height:18px;\"></span> \n</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"font-family:&quot;font-size:14px;vertical-align:baseline;color:#666666;text-indent:24pt;background:white;\">\n	<span style=\"font-style:inherit;font-family:&quot;font-size:13.5pt;vertical-align:baseline;font-weight:inherit;line-height:27px;\">1</span><span style=\"font-style:inherit;font-family:宋体;font-size:13.5pt;vertical-align:baseline;font-weight:inherit;line-height:27px;\">、初试</span><span style=\"font-style:inherit;font-family:inherit;font-size:9pt;vertical-align:baseline;font-weight:inherit;line-height:18px;\"></span> \n</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"font-family:&quot;font-size:14px;vertical-align:baseline;color:#666666;background:white;\">\n	<span style=\"font-style:inherit;font-family:&quot;font-size:13.5pt;vertical-align:baseline;font-weight:inherit;line-height:27px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-style:inherit;font-family:宋体;font-size:13.5pt;vertical-align:baseline;font-weight:inherit;line-height:27px;\">初试时间：</span><span style=\"font-style:inherit;font-family:&quot;font-size:13.5pt;vertical-align:baseline;font-weight:inherit;line-height:27px;\">2015</span><span style=\"font-style:inherit;font-family:宋体;font-size:13.5pt;vertical-align:baseline;font-weight:inherit;line-height:27px;\">年</span><span style=\"font-style:inherit;font-family:&quot;font-size:13.5pt;vertical-align:baseline;font-weight:inherit;line-height:27px;\">4</span><span style=\"font-style:inherit;font-family:宋体;font-size:13.5pt;vertical-align:baseline;font-weight:inherit;line-height:27px;\">月</span><span style=\"font-style:inherit;font-family:&quot;font-size:13.5pt;vertical-align:baseline;font-weight:inherit;line-height:27px;\">1</span><span style=\"font-style:inherit;font-family:宋体;font-size:13.5pt;vertical-align:baseline;font-weight:inherit;line-height:27px;\">1</span><span style=\"font-style:inherit;font-family:宋体;font-size:13.5pt;vertical-align:baseline;font-weight:inherit;line-height:27px;\">日至</span><span style=\"font-style:inherit;font-family:&quot;font-size:13.5pt;vertical-align:baseline;font-weight:inherit;line-height:27px;\">4</span><span style=\"font-style:inherit;font-family:宋体;font-size:13.5pt;vertical-align:baseline;font-weight:inherit;line-height:27px;\">月</span><span style=\"font-style:inherit;font-family:&quot;font-size:13.5pt;vertical-align:baseline;font-weight:inherit;line-height:27px;\">1</span><span style=\"font-style:inherit;font-family:宋体;font-size:13.5pt;vertical-align:baseline;font-weight:inherit;line-height:27px;\">2</span><span style=\"font-style:inherit;font-family:宋体;font-size:13.5pt;vertical-align:baseline;font-weight:inherit;line-height:27px;\">日，具体安排详见准考证。</span><span style=\"font-style:inherit;font-family:inherit;font-size:9pt;vertical-align:baseline;font-weight:inherit;line-height:18px;\"></span> \n</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"font-family:&quot;font-size:14px;vertical-align:baseline;color:#666666;text-indent:24pt;background:white;\">\n	<span style=\"font-style:inherit;font-family:宋体;font-size:13.5pt;vertical-align:baseline;font-weight:inherit;line-height:27px;\">初试科目：政治理论课（获得硕士学位者和应届硕士毕业生免考</span><span style=\"font-style:inherit;font-family:&quot;font-size:13.5pt;vertical-align:baseline;font-weight:inherit;line-height:27px;\">,</span><span style=\"font-style:inherit;font-family:宋体;font-size:13.5pt;vertical-align:baseline;font-weight:inherit;line-height:27px;\">参考书为：《中国特色社会主义理论与实践研究》</span><span style=\"font-style:inherit;font-family:&quot;font-size:13.5pt;vertical-align:baseline;font-weight:inherit;line-height:27px;\">(2013</span><span style=\"font-style:inherit;font-family:宋体;font-size:13.5pt;vertical-align:baseline;font-weight:inherit;line-height:27px;\">年修订版</span><span style=\"font-style:inherit;font-family:&quot;font-size:13.5pt;vertical-align:baseline;font-weight:inherit;line-height:27px;\">)&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-style:inherit;font-family:宋体;font-size:13.5pt;vertical-align:baseline;font-weight:inherit;line-height:27px;\">高等教育出版社</span><span style=\"font-style:inherit;font-family:&quot;font-size:13.5pt;vertical-align:baseline;font-weight:inherit;line-height:27px;\">2013</span><span style=\"font-style:inherit;font-family:宋体;font-size:13.5pt;vertical-align:baseline;font-weight:inherit;line-height:27px;\">年</span><span style=\"font-style:inherit;font-family:&quot;font-size:13.5pt;vertical-align:baseline;font-weight:inherit;line-height:27px;\">8</span><span style=\"font-style:inherit;font-family:宋体;font-size:13.5pt;vertical-align:baseline;font-weight:inherit;line-height:27px;\">月）、外国语（不指定参考书，具体情况可参看附件《东北大学博士研究生入学考试外国语科目考试规定》）、两门业务课。考试采用闭卷笔试的方式，每门科目考试时间为</span><span style=\"font-style:inherit;font-family:&quot;font-size:13.5pt;vertical-align:baseline;font-weight:inherit;line-height:27px;\">3</span><span style=\"font-style:inherit;font-family:宋体;font-size:13.5pt;vertical-align:baseline;font-weight:inherit;line-height:27px;\">小时。</span><span style=\"font-style:inherit;font-family:inherit;font-size:9pt;vertical-align:baseline;font-weight:inherit;line-height:18px;\"></span> \n</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"font-family:&quot;font-size:14px;vertical-align:baseline;color:#666666;text-indent:24pt;background:white;\">\n	<span style=\"font-style:inherit;font-family:&quot;font-size:13.5pt;vertical-align:baseline;font-weight:inherit;line-height:27px;\">2</span><span style=\"font-style:inherit;font-family:宋体;font-size:13.5pt;vertical-align:baseline;font-weight:inherit;line-height:27px;\">、复试</span><span style=\"font-style:inherit;font-family:inherit;font-size:9pt;vertical-align:baseline;font-weight:inherit;line-height:18px;\"></span> \n</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"font-family:&quot;font-size:14px;vertical-align:baseline;color:#666666;text-indent:27pt;background:white;\">\n	<span style=\"font-style:inherit;font-family:宋体;font-size:13.5pt;vertical-align:baseline;font-weight:inherit;line-height:27px;\">复试主要是考查考生综合运用所学知识的能力；测试外语听力、口语能力和专业外语水平；考评考生提供的硕士阶段成绩单、硕士学位论文和评议书等材料；考查考生思想政治表现、业务素质等。复试备有详细记录，并由复试小组给出评语和成绩。复试阶段对同等学力考生加试（笔试）报考专业的两门硕士学位主干课程。加试科目成绩和复试成绩不及格的考生，不予录取。复试时间另行通知。</span><span style=\"font-style:inherit;font-family:inherit;font-size:9pt;vertical-align:baseline;font-weight:inherit;line-height:18px;\"></span> \n</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"font-family:&quot;font-size:14px;vertical-align:baseline;color:#666666;text-indent:27.1pt;background:white;\">\n	<span style=\"font-style:inherit;font-family:宋体;font-size:13.5pt;vertical-align:baseline;font-weight:inherit;line-height:27px;\">考生参加初试时务请携带复试材料，以便向复试小组提交。复试材料包括：硕士阶段的学习成绩单（要求同上）和硕士学位论文及其评议书（应届毕业硕士生提供论文大纲）、专家推荐材料、自我评价材料；公开发表（出版）的论文（专著）、学习（工作）中获奖证书等材料。复试小组将对以上申请材料进行评估，评估结果作为考核和录取的重要依据。</span><span style=\"font-style:inherit;font-family:inherit;font-size:9pt;vertical-align:baseline;font-weight:inherit;line-height:18px;\"></span> \n</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"font-family:&quot;font-size:14px;vertical-align:baseline;color:#666666;text-indent:27.1pt;background:white;\">\n	<b><span style=\"font-style:inherit;font-family:宋体;font-size:13.5pt;vertical-align:baseline;font-weight:inherit;line-height:27px;\">七、体格检查</span></b><span style=\"font-style:inherit;font-family:inherit;font-size:9pt;vertical-align:baseline;font-weight:inherit;line-height:18px;\"></span> \n</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"font-family:&quot;font-size:14px;vertical-align:baseline;color:#666666;text-indent:27pt;background:white;\">\n	<span style=\"font-style:inherit;font-family:宋体;font-size:13.5pt;vertical-align:baseline;font-weight:inherit;line-height:27px;\">初试结束后由学校统一组织体检工作，与复试工作同步进行，体检标准参照教育部、卫生部、中国残疾人联合会制定的《普通高等学校招生体检工作指导意见》和学校有关规定执行。</span><span style=\"font-style:inherit;font-family:inherit;font-size:9pt;vertical-align:baseline;font-weight:inherit;line-height:18px;\"></span> \n</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"font-family:&quot;font-size:14px;vertical-align:baseline;color:#666666;text-indent:27.1pt;background:white;\">\n	<br />\n</p>','sysadmin','2017-02-13 13:42:24','sysadmin','2017-02-20 14:07:10',NULL,NULL),('21071302-f71a-11e6-827e-005056bf3cd7','f9f94fe6-c039-11e6-9c1a-00ac7dc2f176','建筑讲坛（第六讲）香港中文大学建筑学院朱竞翔副教授','','2015-07-13 00:00:00',NULL,'韩丰琨','','是','否','<h1 style=\"text-align:center;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:24px;\">建筑讲坛（第六讲）香港中文大学建筑学院朱竞翔副教授</span> \n</h1>\n<div>\n	<p style=\"background-color:white;text-indent:32.15pt;\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">7月13日，香港中文大学建筑学院副教授、著名建筑师朱竞翔来到东北大学建筑学馆，为建筑学院师生做了一场题为“小而大的天地——轻量建筑的乡村与自然实践”的学术讲座。</span> \n	</p>\n	<p style=\"background-color:white;text-indent:24pt;\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">朱竞翔教授是学院派与实验建筑师群体的代表人物之一，是首批在国际舞台亮相的中国独立建筑师。朱教授专注于研究环保型建筑、新型的空间结构、轻质建筑物料以及地方建造传统的记录和整理。</span> \n	</p>\n	<p style=\"background-color:white;text-indent:24pt;\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">朱教授首先从汶川地震灾难发生后房屋破坏与重建的问题引出本次演讲的主题，介绍了他和他的团队在轻型复合房屋体系的研究与实践，以及这些项目具体的建造过程，并探讨了人们与自然需要怎样的建筑，公共项目的建造如何能够成为凝聚多种力量重建社区的契机等话题，让同学们领略到了建筑建造的魅力与奇妙之处。朱教授还讲到，建筑应结合设计、造价和工程等多方面因素，每一个因素都要相互协调，发挥最大的效用，同学们由此对建筑设计有了新的认识。最后的提问环节同学们针对在设计方面遇到的问题向朱教授提问，朱教授都一一耐心解答了同学们的困惑。</span> \n	</p>\n	<p style=\"background-color:white;text-indent:24pt;\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">得益于朱竞翔教授在百忙之中为大家带来一场精彩的建筑盛宴，使同学们在建筑结构与建筑环境等多个方面有了进一步认识，并对未来的专业学习更加憧憬，可谓获益匪浅。</span> \n	</p>\n</div>','sysadmin','2017-02-20 11:10:34','sysadmin','2017-02-20 11:11:12',NULL,NULL),('215e1c7c-f1ae-11e6-8689-005056bf3cd7','d78fff10-c10c-11e6-a722-00ac7dc2f176','孙贺','专职教师','2017-02-13 00:00:00',NULL,NULL,'已通过','是','是','<h1 style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#ffffff;font-family:verdana, sans-serif;\">\n	<br />\n</h1>\n<div style=\"background-color:#ffffff;font-family:verdana, sans-serif;font-size:13px;\">\n</div>\n<table style=\"width:517pt;border-collapse:collapse;\" class=\"ke-zeroborder\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"690\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td class=\"xl68\" height=\"126\" rowspan=\"7\" width=\"546\" colspan=\"6\">\n				<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">　</span>\n			</td>\n			<td class=\"xl71\" rowspan=\"13\" width=\"144\" colspan=\"2\">\n				<img title=\"\" alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.jz.neu.edu.cn/kindeditor-4.1.9/attached/image/20140308/20140308140152_9605.jpg\" width=\"150\" height=\"223\" />\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\