知','','2016-12-21 00:00:00',NULL,'王建东','研究生考核','是','否','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#000000;font-family:&quot;font-size:12px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;text-align:start;background-color:#FFFFFF;text-indent:30pt;\">\n	&nbsp;\n</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#000000;font-family:&quot;font-size:12px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;text-align:start;background-color:#FFFFFF;text-indent:30pt;\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;font-size:15pt;\">为做好<span>2017</span>年以申请考核制方式攻读我校博士学位研究生考核相关工作，现将有关事项通知如下：<span></span></span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#000000;font-family:&quot;font-size:12px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;text-align:start;background-color:#FFFFFF;text-indent:15.05pt;\">\n	<b><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;font-size:15pt;\">&nbsp; 一、外语笔试考核<span></span></span></b>\n</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#000000;font-family:&quot;font-size:12px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;text-align:start;background-color:#FFFFFF;text-indent:15pt;\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;font-size:15pt;\">&nbsp; 1</span><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;font-size:15pt;\">．考试时间：<span>11</span>月<span>30</span>日下午<span>14</span>：<span>00</span>—<span>17</span>：<span>00</span>。<span></span></span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#000000;font-family:&quot;font-size:12px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;text-align:start;background-color:#FFFFFF;text-indent:15pt;\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;font-size:15pt;\">&nbsp; 2</span><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;font-size:15pt;\">．考试地点：东北大学冶金馆中心考场。<span></span></span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#000000;font-family:&quot;font-size:12px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;text-align:start;background-color:#FFFFFF;text-indent:15pt;\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;font-size:15pt;\">&nbsp; 3</span><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;font-size:15pt;\">．请参加外语笔试考核（不符合外语免考条件）的考生携带身份证、学生证及必备的文具，提前<span>30</span>分钟，到考场等候。<span></span></span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#000000;font-family:&quot;font-size:12px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n	<b><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;font-size:15pt;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span></span></span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;font-size:15pt;\">外语笔试考核成绩未达到学校要求者，不予录取。<span></span></span></b>\n</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#000000;font-family:&quot;font-size:12px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;text-align:start;background-color:#FFFFFF;text-indent:30.1pt;\">\n	<b><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;font-size:15pt;\">二、学院综合考核<span></span></span></b>\n</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#000000;font-family:&quot;font-size:12px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;text-align:left;text-indent:28pt;background:white;\" align=\"left\">\n	<span style=\"line-height:28px;font-family:楷体_GB2312;font-size:14pt;\">学院综合考核由专业基础知识、科研能力和综合素质三部分组成，每部分满分为<span>100</span>分，各部分成绩均在<span>60</span>分以上的考生为合格考生，不合格考生不得录取。</span><span style=\"line-height:24px;font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#000000;font-family:&quot;font-size:12px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;text-align:start;background-color:#FFFFFF;text-indent:30pt;\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;font-size:15pt;\">学院综合考核的内容、方式、时间、地点、等内容详见各学院网站工作细则（陆续公布中）。<span></span></span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#000000;font-family:&quot;font-size:12px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;text-align:start;background-color:#FFFFFF;text-indent:30pt;\">\n	<b><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;font-size:15pt;\">三、监督举报电话</span></b><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;font-size:15pt;\"></span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#000000;font-family:&quot;font-size:12px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;text-align:start;background-color:#FFFFFF;text-indent:15pt;\